1. *Straža* je noćas bila vrlo budna. (The guard was very alert tonight.)
2. Vojska ima zaduženje da održava *stražu* na granici. (The army is responsible for keeping watch at the border.)
3. Narednik je postavio vojnike u *stražarske* toranj. (The sergeant stationed soldiers in the guard tower.)
4. Jedan od zadataka vatrogasne *straže* je da spriječi širenje vatre. (One of the tasks of the fire brigade is to prevent the spread of fire.)
5. *Straža* je bila smještena u maloj kućici na kraju puta. (The guard was housed in a small cottage at the end of the road.)
6. Bez *straže*, nema sigurnosti. (Without guards, there is no security.)
7. Vojska će slati *straže* na teren svakih nekoliko sati. (The army will send guards to the field every few hours.)
8. Naš *stražar* je spavao pa su lopovi uspjeli proći. (Our guard was sleeping so the thieves managed to pass.)
9. Kapetan je naredio *stražaru* da ostane na svom mjestu. (The captain ordered the guard to stay in place.)
10. *Stražari* su stajali u stražarskoj kućici i motrili na okolinu. (The guards stood in the guardhouse and watched the surroundings.)